INSERT INTO feedback_reviews (review_text) VALUES 
('I had been looking for a residential plot in Kurukshetra for over six months but was confused by the fluctuating rates and unclear paperwork shown by other dealers. A friend suggested Landmark Properties, and honestly, the difference was clear from day one. They showed me genuine options in developed sectors with clear titles. Today, I am a proud owner of a plot in a gated society. Highly recommended for their transparency!'),
('Selling a property can be a headache, especially when you are not living in the city. I wanted to sell my commercial shop near Pipli Road while being based in Delhi. Landmark Properties handled everything efficiently. They found a buyer, negotiated a fair price, and managed the documentation so smoothly that I only had to travel once for the final signature. Truly professional service.'),
('My experience with Landmark Properties has been exceptional. I was looking for an investment opportunity with good returns in Haryana. Their team analyzed the market trends and suggested a few upcoming areas in Kurukshetra. I went ahead with their advice, and within a year, the property value has appreciated significantly. They really know the pulse of the real estate market.'),
('Finding a rental house that fits your budget and preferences is not easy. I visited multiple agencies, but most showed me rundown places or demanded high brokerage. Landmark Properties was different. They understood my requirement for a 2BHK near the university and showed me three great options immediately. The process was quick, and I moved in within a week. Very helpful staff!'),
('As an NRI, buying property in India feels risky due to lack of transparency. Landmark Properties changed that perception for me. I managed to buy a residential plot in Sector 10 completely remotely until the final registration. They shared video tours, legal verification reports, and kept me updated daily. Trustworthy and reliable property consultants.'),
('I wanted to buy agricultural land near Pehowa for farming purposes. Most dealers were trying to sell me disputed lands or charging exorbitant commissions. Landmark Properties gave me honest advice and showed me verified lands with clear records. They even helped me understand the soil quality and water availability. Genuine people to deal with.'),
('Great service! I was looking for a showroom space for my new retail business in Kurukshetra. Location was my top priority. The team at Landmark Properties showed me some exclusive SCOs that were not listed on online portals. I got a prime location at a very competitive rate. Thanks to them, my business is getting great footfall now.'),
('I recently purchased a floor in Thanesar through Landmark Properties. The best part was their transparency regarding the construction quality and legal approvals. They didn''t hide anything and answered all my queries patiently. It felt like I was taking advice from an elder brother rather than a broker. Five stars for their honesty!'),
('If you are new to Kurukshetra and don''t know the property market, don''t go anywhere else. I wasted two months with local brokers who just wanted to close the deal anyhow. Landmark Properties took the time to understand my needs. They guided me on which sectors represent better value for money. I am very happy with my purchase.'),
('The team at Landmark Properties is very professional. I needed to sell my ancestral land, which had some paperwork issues. Other agents refused to touch it, but Landmark''s legal team helped me sort out the documents first and then found a buyer. It took some time, but they got the job done cleanly. Highly appreciate their support.'),
('I was hesitant about investing in real estate because of the scams we hear about. But meeting the owner of Landmark Properties gave me confidence. They operate with full integrity. I bought a small plot for my daughter''s future, and the registration process was completely hassle-free. No hidden charges, no last-minute surprises.'),
('We wanted a house near the new bus stand for better connectivity. Landmark Properties showed us some resale options that were in excellent condition. They negotiated with the seller on our behalf and saved us a good amount. If you want a fair deal without the typical broker nonsense, this is the place.'),
('I have been dealing in properties for the last 10 years, and I can say Landmark Properties is one of the few organized players in Kurukshetra. Their office environment is professional, and they use modern tools to showcase properties. Their staff is well-trained and polite. A pleasant change from the usual property dealers.'),
('Buying a home is a dream for everyone, and Landmark Properties helped me fulfill mine. I had a limited budget, but I didn''t want to compromise on the locality. They worked hard to find a seller who was willing to negotiate. I am now living in a beautiful colony, thanks to their efforts.'),
('I needed a large warehouse space for my logistics business on the highway. Landmark Properties has an extensive network and showed me multiple options within two days. They helped me finalize the lease terms that were favorable for my business. Quick and efficient service!'),
('What I like about Landmark Properties is that they don''t push you to buy. They give you the facts, the pros and cons of each property, and let you decide. I visited their office multiple times before finalizing a plot, and they were always patient and welcoming. That''s how you build long-term relationships.'),
('I bought a commercial plot through them in 2021, and recently I sold it through them as well. Both times, the experience was smooth. They handle the entire lifecycle of the property deal, so you don''t have to run around for NOCs or court paperwork. They handle it all.'),
('My parents wanted to shift to Kurukshetra from a village. We needed a safe and peaceful locality. Landmark Properties understood our concern and showed us houses in gated communities with good security. My parents are very happy with the neighborhood. Thank you for caring about your customers.'),
('I was looking for a property exchange deal – wanted to sell my flat and buy a bigger plot. Such deals are complicated, but Landmark Properties managed it beautifully. They synchronized both the sale and purchase so I didn''t face any fund shortage. Expert coordinators!'),
('Reliable, Honest, and Fast. These three words describe Landmark Properties. I had an urgent requirement to buy a shop as my previous lease was expiring. They prioritized my request and found me a better location within a week. I saved my business from interruption.'),
('Landmark Properties helped me verify the documents of a property I was buying from a relative. Even though they were not the direct brokers, they offered their consultation service for a nominal fee to ensure I wasn''t being cheated. That shows their commitment to ethical practices.'),
('We are a group of friends who wanted to invest together in a large chunk of land for future plotting. Landmark Properties identified a high-potential agricultural zone near the proposed highway. Their foresight was amazing – rates have already started jumping there. Best investment advisors in town.'),
('I had a bad experience with another dealer who took my token money and never showed the documents. I came to Landmark Properties very skeptical. They not only helped me find a new property but also guided me on how to legally recover my money from the previous agent. True professionals.'),
('For anyone looking for premium properties in Kurukshetra, this is the go-to agency. They have exclusive inventory that you won''t find on common listings. I bought a luxury villa through them, and the discretion and professionalism they maintained were top-notch.'),
('Their after-sales service is commendable. After I bought the plot, I needed help with boundary wall construction and electricity connection. The team at Landmark Properties connected me with reliable contractors and helped me get the meters installed. They don''t just leave you after the deal.'),
('I recommended Landmark Properties to my colleague for a rental requirement, and he thanked me later. He said they showed him exactly what he wanted without wasting time on irrelevant properties. Consistency in service is their biggest strength.'),
('Investing in HUDA sectors can be tricky with transfer fees and enhancement costs. The team at Landmark explained every single cost involved before I signed the deal. No hidden costs at all. I knew exactly what I was paying for. Transparency is 100%.'),
('I wanted to sell my property in Ambala to buy one in Kurukshetra. They have a good network in both cities. They managed to sell my Ambala property at a good market rate and simultaneously booked the new one here. It was a seamless transition for my family.'),
('The staff are very polite and educated. They speak clearly and don’t use aggressive sales tactics. I felt very comfortable discussing my finances and requirements with them. A very decent and family-friendly atmosphere at their office.'),
('Landmark Properties is the reason I have a strong portfolio today. I started with a small investment 5 years ago on their advice, and rolled over the profits into bigger properties. They have been my growth partners in real estate.'),
('I had a specific requirement for a north-facing plot due to Vastu reasons. Many agents dismissed it saying it''s hard to find. Landmark Properties respected my belief and filtered out only north-facing options. I found the perfect Vastu-compliant plot thanks to them.'),
('They act as a perfect bridge between buyers and sellers. I felt the negotiation was very fair. Both parties were happy with the final price. Usually, brokers try to squeeze one side, but here it was a win-win deal. Fair trade practices indeed.'),
('Dealing with NRI properties requires specific paperwork and tax compliances. Landmark Properties has a specialized team for this. They handled the trusted TDS and repatriation formalities for my purchase from an NRI seller. I didn''t have to worry about a single legal compliance.'),
('I am a retired government employee and wanted to invest my retirement funds safely. Safety was my only concern. Landmark Properties showed me only government-approved colonies and HUDA plots. I sleep peacefully knowing my life savings are invested in a secure asset.'),
('The best thing is their availability. Whenever I called them for a query, even on weekends, they responded. They value their client''s time and anxiety levels during a property deal. Excellent communication skills.'),
('I was looking for a plot near the new bypass road. They showed me the future development plans for that area which convinced me to invest. Their research about city planning and future infrastructure is impressive. They don''t just sell land, they sell a vision.'),
('My wife and I had different opinions on what kind of house to buy. The agent at Landmark sat down with us, listened to both our perspectives, and found a middle ground—a duplex that satisfied both our needs. Great mediation skills!'),
('They have a wide range of options for every budget. I thought they only deal in luxury properties, but they helped me find a small affordable plot for my shop as well. They treat small and big clients with equal respect.'),
('The documentation team at Landmark Properties is flawless. They checked the chain of deeds for the last 30 years for the property I was buying to ensure there were no claims. That level of due diligence is rare.'),
('I booked a flat through them in a society under construction. They helped me get the payment plan customized according to my cash flow. They have good relations with builders and can get you deals that you might not get directly.'),
('If you want to buy property in Kurukshetra, Karnal or nearby, just blindly trust Landmark Properties. I have done more than 5 deals with them in the last 4 years for my extended family. Never faced a single issue.'),
('I was struggling to get a loan sanctioned for a property purchase. Landmark Properties has tied up with major banks and their loan executive got my file processed in record time. They provide end-to-end solutions.'),
('They helped me lease out my building to a corporate client. I was looking for a long-term tenant with a lock-in period. They found a reputed bank to lease the ground floor. Very happy with the rental income I am getting now.'),
('Honesty is their policy. There was a slight issue with the measurement of a plot I liked. Instead of hiding it, they informed me upfront and got it corrected from the revenue department before the registry. That saved me from future disputes.'),
('I searched online, looked at newspaper ads, and called many numbers. Finally, a visit to Landmark Properties office solved my problem. They have the largest inventory of direct seller properties in this region.'),
('Their guidance on commercial real estate is top-notch. They told me which market is shifting and where the new commercial hub will be. I bought a shop based on their advice, and the rates have already gone up by 20%.'),
('My experience was smooth and stress-free. Real estate jargon can be confusing, but they explained everything in simple language. From agreement to sell to the final sale deed, they were with me at the tehsil office.'),
('I appreciate their patience. I am a picky buyer and saw over 20 properties before finalizing one. They never got annoyed and kept showing me options with a smile until I was satisfied. 10/10 for customer service.'),
('Landmark Properties helps you build assets. Their advice is always focused on long-term wealth creation rather than quick commission. I trust their judgement more than my own when it comes to property trends in Haryana.'),
('A truly professional real estate firm. They have a proper office, dedicated staff for legal, sales, and accounts. It feels safe depositing token money with them compared to fly-by-night property dealers.'),
('I wanted a farm house for weekend getaways. They showed me some beautiful locations near the canal with greenery and peaceful surroundings. It was exactly what I had in mind. They made my dream come true.'),
('We sold our house to move abroad. We were on a tight schedule. Landmark Properties expedited the process, found a cash-ready buyer, and completed the formalities in 10 days. We could fly out peacefully knowing the deal was done.'),
('They are very transparent about their brokerage charges. No hidden cuts or commissions from the other party. Everything is on the table. This ethical way of working will take them a long way.'),
('I bought a plot for my son''s factory. Industrial plots have complex zoning laws. Landmark Properties guided us through the CLU (Change of Land Use) process and zoning regulations perfectly. Very knowledgeable team.'),
('Kurukshetra is growing fast, and Landmark Properties is leading the change in how real estate is traded here. Organized, efficient, and customer-centric. I wish them all the best.'),
('One of the few agents who give realistic price estimates. Others quoted inflated prices just to get my listing, but Landmark gave a market-correct valuation which helped my property sell faster.'),
('I had a dispute with a previous builder regarding possession. Landmark Properties intervened and used their goodwill to help me get my possession letter. They go out of their way to help clients.'),
('Great for rental services. They verify the tenant''s background thoroughly, which is very important for safety. I rented my first floor through them and got a very decent family as tenants.'),
('Top class service. The virtual tour they sent me of the property was so detailed I didn''t feel the need to visit physically initially. Technology usage is good.'),
('They respect your budget constraints. I told them my max limit, and they never tried to pressure me into seeing properties above that. They respect the client''s financial boundaries.'),
('I found them via a Google search and saw good reviews. Now I am writing one myself. They totally live up to the reputation. Honest, transparent, and quick.'),
('Buying land is a sentimental decision for us Indians. Landmark Properties team respects that emotion. They made the registry day special for our family. It was a celebration.'),
('If you are looking for properties in Sector 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9 or 10, they have the best options available. They seem to rule the market in these prime sectors.'),
('I was renting for 10 years. They showed me a calculation of how buying with a home loan would be cheaper than paying rent in the long run. That advice changed my life. I am building equity now instead of losing money on rent.'),
('Very clear communication. They kept me in the loop at every stage of the negotiation. I never felt left out or uninformed. Excellent client management.'),
('They have a good network of architects and builders too. After buying the plot, I hired a builder recommended by them, and the house construction is going great. A complete ecosystem.'),
('I was looking for a conflict-free property. They checked court records and ensured the land was free from any litigation. Peace of mind is priceless, and they delivered that.'),
('Friendly, approachable, and professional. The Director himself met us to finalize the deal. It shows they care about every customer, big or small.'),
('The best thing is they don''t disappear after the deal. I call them even now for small advice on property tax or maintenance, and they always help. Relationship building is their motto.'),
('I invested in a pre-launch commercial project through them. Usually risky, but with Landmark''s backing, I was confident. The project is nearing completion, and prices have doubled. Great tip!'),
('They helped me consolidate my scattered land parcels into one big farm. It was a complex consolidation process involving multiple owners. They handled the coordination beautifully.'),
('I am 100% satisfied. If I buy property again, it will only be through Landmark Properties. They are the benchmark for real estate services in this district.'),
('They helped me negotiate a tough deal. The seller was very rigid, but the agent from Landmark used his skills to bring down the price to a level we both agreed on. Smart negotiators.'),
('Clean paperwork is their USP. In real estate, documents are everything. They are meticulous about checking every stamp and signature. You are in safe hands.'),
('We were looking for a retirement home. Quiet, accessible, and safe. They showed us a colony that was perfect for seniors. We are enjoying our retired life here.'),
('Fastest deal of my life. Saw the property on Monday, liked it, tokens paid on Tuesday, agreement on Wednesday. When you work with pros, things move fast.'),
('They know the history of every colony in Kurukshetra. They told me which areas have water logging issues and which don''t. That inside info saved me from a bad investment.'),
('I wanted to gift a plot to my wife on our anniversary. They kept the surprise, managed the paperwork discreetly, and handed over the papers on the special day. Thank you team!'),
('Their understanding of Vastu, location benefits, and construction costs is amazing. You get a free consultation on all these aspects when you deal with them.'),
('I bought a shop in the main market. The rental yield is exactly what they promised. No false commitments. They deliver what they say.'),
('Professional environment. They have a proper conference room for meetings, which makes the closing process very formal and comfortable. No roadside dealings.'),
('My friend recommended them, and I am glad he did. In the jungle of property dealers, Landmark Properties is a safe haven. Good people, good work.'),
('I was looking for agriculture land for organic farming. They found me a patch with good groundwater and fertile soil. They understand different needs of different clients.'),
('From site visit to registry, they provide transportation and assistance. Very courteous staff. They treat you like a guest.'),
('They resolved a long-pending dispute on my father''s property and helped us sell it. We had lost hope, but they made it happen. Miracle workers.'),
('If you want premium plots in Urban Estate or HUDA sectors, they have the best inventory. I think they capture the market before anyone else knows.'),
('Honest feedback on my property. They managed my expectations on the selling price instead of agreeing to a high price just to please me. That honesty helped me sell it faster.'),
('They helped me interpret the Master Plan of Kurukshetra city. I invested in an area marked for future commercial zone. That insight was valuable.'),
('I felt very safe dealing with them. Complete transparency in money matters. All payments were through cheque/RTGS. No cash mess.'),
('They are a blessing for people who don''t have time to run around government offices. They have a team that handles the legwork for you.'),
('I bought a corner plot which is considered premium. They got me a good deal on the PLC (Preferential Location Charges). Very happy.'),
('Real estate is all about trust. Landmark Properties has earned mine. I refer them to all my friends and family.'),
('Simply the best in the business. Professional, knowledgeable, and reliable. Keep up the good work Landmark team!'),
('I wanted a low-budget plot for a small house. They didn''t ignore me because of my small budget. They found me a decent colony within my range. Respect for that.'),
('Great experience. I will definitely come back for my next investment. Kurukshetra market means Landmark Properties.'),
('They helped me identify a fake seller who provided forged documents. They saved my 50 Lakhs. I owe them big time. Always check with Landmark before buying.'),
('The variety of properties they have is huge. You don''t need to visit 10 dealers. Just one visit to Landmark is enough to see the whole market.'),
('Smooth, transparent, and profitable. My definition of a deal with Landmark Properties. Highly recommended.')
